Package net.bubbaland.trivia.client.dialog

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddTabDialog
    Creates a dialog that allows the user to select a tab to be added to the tabbed pane.
    AddTabDialog.TabCompare
    Customer comparator to sort tabs in the appropriate order.
    CloseQuestionDialog
    Creates a dialog box that prompts user for the correct answer when closing a question.
    ConflictDialog
    Creates a dialog notifying user of a scoring discrepancy between the announced score and the calculated score.
    EditQuestionDialog  
    LoadStateDialog
    Creates a dialog that lists the saves and prompts for one to load.
    NewQuestionDialog
    Creates a prompt to enter new question data.
    OperatorDialog
    Creates a dialog that asks for the operator to confirm a correct answer.
    ResetQuestionDialog  
    TriviaDialog
    Custom dialog that handles setting up a lot of the characteristics used by all trivia dialogs.
    TriviaDialogPanel
    Super-class for most of the dialog box panels in the trivia GUI.
    UserLoginDialog
    Creates prompt for user name.
    ViewAnswerDialog
    Create a dialog to display answer data.
    ViewQuestionDialog
    Create a dialog that displays question data.
    WaitDialog
